original_title: Girls Aloud: Ten - The Hits Tour
overview: The British pop act captured live in performance on their final UK tour in March 2013. The tour was in support of the group's second greatest hits album, 'Ten' (2012), and saw them perform tracks including 'Sound of the Underground', 'Love Machine', 'Jump', 'Biology' and 'The Promise'. Following the completion of the tour, the group announced that they had split.
title: Girls Aloud: Ten - The Hits Tour
